{"type": "article", "id": 10396, "title": "皮卡丘帽子", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-04T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235558oR9Xn6jZe3I8Aiar.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">Pokémon by BEAMS &amp; New Era</span>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">日本经典游戏《Pokémon》即将迎来其 20 岁生日，为此其官方邀请 BEAMS 和 New Era 联手推出了一个帽子系列，其设计主题是广受全世界人们喜爱的皮卡丘。在配色上，选用了皮卡丘经典黄色以及海军蓝色，趣味盎然。产品将于本月末上市。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235556D1KsjX2NcWVGLpb7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235557F3Opg9E0yRBisJVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235557UinSMarD7lhQv3p2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235558CMadQbgnf4Vy6RSZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66410256\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}